  "text": "The study from 1994 was part of an international survey on iodine deficiency in Europe (Thyromobil Project) [CITATION_1] , while that from 1999 was part of a nationwide survey on the effectiveness of iodine prophylaxis in Poland [CITATION_2] . Studies in 2010 [CITATION_3] and 2016 were carried out within the project carried out by the Polish Mother's Memorial Hospital -Research Institute in Lodz. All studies were performed by employees of the same endocrinology department.",
